{"title":"hexo+inside博客个性化定制","date":"2020-04-02T16:00:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年4月3日","L":"2020/04/03","MM-DD":"04-03"},"thumbnail":"https://sansui-1259687493.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/%E6%9D%82%E5%9B%BE/7bf2ee993c7a83631b0fc0ea8fabb16e.jpg?q-sign-algorithm=sha1&q-ak=AKIDNc6bP0CQj08LPELw7i6GB1c8OODnaD2c&q-sign-time=1585890642;3601585887042&q-key-time=1585890642;3601585887042&q-header-list=&q-url-param-list=&q-signature=a7ada497dc5fbf4593a16b7b997c4e97e8668b90","link":"2020/04/03/hexo-inside博客个性化定制","comments":true,"tags":["Hexo","Inside"],"categories":["Hexo"],"updated":"2020-04-27T08:40:23.693Z","content":"<h1 id=\"主题界面美化\">主题界面美化<a href=\"#主题界面美化\" title=\"主题界面美化\"></a></h1><hr>\n<h2 id=\"半透明美化\">半透明美化<a href=\"#半透明美化\" title=\"半透明美化\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://sansui-1259687493.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/INSIDE%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E5%8D%8A%E9%80%8F%E6%98%8E.png\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /><p>此处背板半透明代码为</p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul><li>tag: style<br>code: |<br>@media screen and (min-width:675px) {<pre><code>.φdx {\n  background-color: rgba(243, 246, 247, .65)!important;\n}</code></pre>}<pre><code>.φdy, .φem {\nbackground-color: rgba(243, 246, 247, .4)!important;</code></pre>}</li></ul></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"插件美化\">插件美化<a href=\"#插件美化\" title=\"插件美化\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"访问统计插件：不蒜子\">访问统计插件：不蒜子<a href=\"#访问统计插件：不蒜子\" title=\"访问统计插件：不蒜子\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://sansui-1259687493.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/INSIDE%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96/%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1.png\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /><p>我使用的是这个：<a href=\"http://ibruce.info/2015/04/04/busuanzi/\" target=\"_blank\">不蒜子统计</a></p>\n<p>先进行<strong>脚本的安装</strong>，再使用不蒜子的页面。</p>\n<p>安装方法：就是主题配置文件 <code>sidebar</code> 模块插入 <code>busuanzi.js</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">_config.yml</span><br><span class=\"line\">-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</span><br><span class=\"line\">plugins:</span><br><span class=\"line\">  - position: sidebar</span><br><span class=\"line\">    template: |</span><br><span class=\"line\">      &lt;script async src&#x3D;&quot;&#x2F;&#x2F;busuanzi.ibruce.info&#x2F;busuanzi&#x2F;2.3&#x2F;busuanzi.pure.mini.js&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>再<strong>安装标签</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_container_site_pv&quot;&gt;本站总访问量&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_value_site_pv&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;次&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_container_site_uv&quot;&gt;本站访客数&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_value_site_uv&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;人次&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>也可以用此</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">busuanzi_value_site_pv：异步回填访问数</span><br><span class=\"line\">busuanzi_container_site_pv：为防止计数服务访问出错或超时（3秒）的情况下，使整个标签自动隐藏显示</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在 <code>_config.yml</code> 文件里找到 <code>footer</code> 下的 <code>custom</code>，写入相关的 html 代码。比如：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">_config.yml</span><br><span class=\"line\"># Custom text.</span><br><span class=\"line\">custom: &lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_container_site_uv&quot; style&#x3D;&#39;display:none&#39;&gt;Total &lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_value_site_uv&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; visitors. &lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_container_site_pv&quot; style&#x3D;&#39;display:none&#39;&gt;&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;busuanzi_value_site_pv&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Views&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"闭关学习计划","link":"2020/04/10/闭关学习计划"},"next":{"title":"HTML学习一（语意化标签 1 ）","link":"2020/03/28/HTML学习（标题标签）"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/04/03/hexo-inside博客个性化定制/","toc":[{"id":"主题界面美化","title":"主题界面美化","index":"1","children":[{"id":"半透明美化","title":"半透明美化","index":"1.1"}]},{"id":"插件美化","title":"插件美化","index":"2","children":[{"id":"访问统计插件：不蒜子","title":"访问统计插件：不蒜子","index":"2.1"}]}]}